    <task id="LOCAL-00037" summary="Implement smart map generation sync and overhaul reroll delays&#10;&#10;- Integrated `wait_for_map_ready` logic from `bs_scores` branch to completely eliminate race conditions and reading partial (zeroed) memory stats.&#10;- Replaced the hardcoded `MAP_LOAD_DELAY` with `MIN_DELAY`. The scanner now dynamically waits for the Unity engine to finish generating the interactables dictionary, using `MIN_DELAY` only for user visual comfort.&#10;- Fixed an issue where the initial map state was ignored upon pressing the start hotkey (added `require_change` and `is_first_scan` logic).&#10;- Refactored sleep logic into non-blocking poll loops with `abort_condition`. The pause hotkey now instantly interrupts long `MIN_DELAY` sleeps.&#10;- Optimized `RESET_HOLD_DURATION` safety buffer (reduced from +0.1s to +0.05s) to speed up the reroll loop.&#10;- Removed obsolete double-read confirmation logic from the background loop since the new state sync guarantees data consistency.">
